<div class="block">
      
  <div class="content">
    <div class="full-title with-title-branding">
      <div class="title-branding"><a href="/taxonomy/term/868"><img src="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/sites/bfi.org.uk/files/styles/16x9_small/public/sight-and-sound-logo-280x69.png?itok=AEegRSbk" alt="" /></a></div>
  
  <h1>
          What I owe to Chris Marker    
    
      </h1>

  
  
        <div class="copy">
              <div class="intro"><p>The Chilean documentarist Patricio Guzmán pays tribute to his late mentor from another planet.</p>
</div>
            
      
              <p class="author-data">
          <span class="author"><a href="/people/patricio-guzm-n"> Patricio  Guzmán  </a></span><br /><span class="date">Updated: <time datetime="2015-02-10">10 February 2015</time></span>        </p>
      
      
          </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="block">
      
  <div class="content">
    
  <ul class="share">
          <li class="facebook_share"><div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news/what-i-owe-chris-marker" data-layout="button_count"></div>
</li>
          <li class="field_tweetbutton"><div class="tweetbutton-tweet tweetbutton"><a href="http://twitter.com/share" data-size="medium" data-count="horizontal" data-via="SightSoundmag" data-related=":" data-text="What I owe to Chris Marker" data-counturl="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news/what-i-owe-chris-marker" data-url="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news/what-i-owe-chris-marker" data-lang="" class="twitter-share-button">Tweet</a></div></li>
          <li class="pinterest"><a href="//pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news/what-i-owe-chris-marker&description=What I owe to Chris Marker&media=https://www2.bfi.org.uk/sites/bfi.org.uk/files/news/first-year-the-1972-002-campesino-del-sur-1000x750.jpg" data-pin-do="buttonPin" data-pin-config="beside" data-pin-zero="true"><img src="//assets.pinterest.com/images/pidgets/pin_it_button.png" /></a></li>
      </ul>

  <div class='social_sidebar'>
  	<ul>
	            <li class="facebook_share"><div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news/what-i-owe-chris-marker" data-layout="box_count"></div>
</li>
		          <li class="field_tweetbutton"><div class="tweetbutton-tweet tweetbutton"><a href="http://twitter.com/share" data-size="medium" data-count="vertical" data-via="SightSoundmag" data-related=":" data-text="What I owe to Chris Marker" data-counturl="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news/what-i-owe-chris-marker" data-url="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news/what-i-owe-chris-marker" data-lang="" class="twitter-share-button">Tweet</a></div></li>
		          <li class="pinterest"><a href="//pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news/what-i-owe-chris-marker&description=What I owe to Chris Marker&media=https://www2.bfi.org.uk/sites/bfi.org.uk/files/news/first-year-the-1972-002-campesino-del-sur-1000x750.jpg" data-pin-do="buttonPin" data-pin-config="above"><img src="//assets.pinterest.com/images/pidgets/pin_it_button.png" /></a></li>
